ABDI SOLTANI: You know, I would
just encourage every Google

00:54:19.330 --> 00:54:21.790
employee, whether you
work here in Mountain

00:54:21.790 --> 00:54:24.880
View at the headquarters or
anywhere in the United States

00:54:24.880 --> 00:54:29.050
or anywhere in the world,
to please be involved.

00:54:29.050 --> 00:54:32.470
I would encourage you to have
a plan around the following

00:54:32.470 --> 00:54:33.050
things.

00:54:33.050 --> 00:54:35.500
One is your
charitable donations.

00:54:35.500 --> 00:54:38.170
